<%#
  General View On This Base Layout Pattern
  ==============================
  EJS does not support layout inheritance. Instead, each page view uses:

    <%- include('../layout/header', { title: 'Page Title' }) %>

    <!-- page content here -->

    <%- include('../layout/footer') %>

  Available locals (set via res.locals on every request):
    - currentUser    : user object or null
    - isAuthenticated: boolean
    - message        : { type: 'success'|'error'|'info', text: '...' } or null
    - csrfToken      : string

  Optional locals for header/footer:
    - extraCss : array of CSS paths, e.g. ['/css/pages/auth.css']
    - extraJs  : array of JS paths,  e.g. ['/js/search.js']
%>
